            <p style="text-align:center; font-size: 130%; margin-left: 10%"><i style="color:darkblue;" class="fa-regular fa-user"></i>We Have Taken All Precautions for You</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:3%; display: flex; padding-bottom: 2%">
